{"tid":1854583,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"打J點解會變聖人mode?","createTime":"2020-01-31T14:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T22:39:29.000Z","uid":93379,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2891da2df9ddd1d4adbf39b152dde6de889a4e03","tid":1854583,"uid":93379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:31:45.000Z","msg":"每次出完火之後個人總係會變得好理性 好有動力去做野<br />\n原本頹到hea 9 9咁都會突然好上進咁<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以解釋到生理/心理上點解會咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔靠出火，又有無其他方法可以做到同樣效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果可以長期keep住，productivity都咪話唔高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc46938a1c74eb065fbe3af858636e32923467ad","tid":1854583,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T22:08:25.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=2e37bb72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=a1d47828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a><br />\n戒J 前後對比圖<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.noj1314.258club.com%2Fforumdisplay.php%3Ffid%3D63&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=29157259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=63</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ需知： <br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ後３個月內症狀加重／加深屬正常，係戒斷反應<br />\n<br />\n身體恢復過程並唔係直線上升，而係好似過山車咁上下移動，會不斷由壞轉好，好轉壞<br />\n但隨著時間既增長，身體會慢慢恢復，症狀慢慢消失<br />\n<br />\n夢遺唔當破戒，意淫都傷身，睇ＡＶ唔Ｊ一樣咁傷身 ，中醫：心動則精自走<br />\n<br />\n做愛都傷身，所以我地戒Ｊ恢復身體，身體好虧既戒返２年，之後再節制性行為，咁就唔會出症狀，飛翔老師推薦一月2次，就是腎氣充足的情況下，這樣對身體傷害較小。<br />\n<br />\n戒色唔係做和尚，係先禁慾養返好個身體，再同老婆／女友節制性生活，咁就唔會出症狀<br />\n<br />\n叫雞係比打丁更加嚴重既邪淫，如果你忍唔到，寧願你打丁，都唔好叫雞<br />\n<br />\n戒丁期間扑野唔算破戒，但你本身既症狀，唔洗諗住會恢復<br />\n<br />\n戒丁最好既方法就係睇戒色文章，想成功戒Ｊ就將（戒為良藥）睇一次<br />\n學習提升覺悟，覺悟降伏心魔，唔睇（戒為良藥），基本上只係等破戒"},{"pid":"18502ab1afecd4a75964f52aed8e22986deb8589","tid":1854583,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T22:10:34.000Z","msg":"因為身體機能要避免你係咁射精<br />\n你諗下射一次消耗左幾多體力"},{"pid":"bf472aafee3fc1ef60621322001b94bdd4827b36","tid":1854583,"uid":268774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T22:22:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d575236b918e6e6e73f316ed134af089f63131e2","tid":1854583,"uid":268774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T22:22:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afa7fa6eab85b1415eb427bb3e92944e0c58f1b9","tid":1854583,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T22:29:05.000Z","msg":"我只係知j完操嘢好力啲"},{"pid":"2699e4d39232ef9e26ef50b43d4f95c0e81ac3dd","tid":1854583,"uid":268774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T22:32:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"424700a9ebb825663febaa661a396f0b907cc6ba","tid":1854583,"uid":99930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf472aafee3fc1ef60621322001b94bdd4827b36","tid":1854583,"uid":268774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T22:22:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T22:37:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">敢做生命前鋒<br />\n無懼甚麼 生死都有功 <br />\n我捱的痛 記的功<br />\n令我鬥志更加雄</span></strong>"},{"pid":"55cf6b22ab75b69129105474a21486da6f04f91c","tid":1854583,"uid":268774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T22:39:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}